attributes.title: IASAS Volleyball Travel
attributes.description:
Created on September 30, 2010 by kerry_dyke on Sourcemap.org:

5-6 teams will come here to ISB this weekend to compete in an IASAS sports event.  The teams come from Jakarta, Taiwan, Manila, SIngapore, and KL.
